amendatorysection.para: The Nebraska Children's Commission shall provide a written report to the Health and Human Services Committee of the Legislature on the status of its activities on or before August 1, 2012, September 15, 2012, and November 1, 2012. The commission shall complete the statewide strategic plan required pursuant to section 43-4204 and provide a written report to the Health and Human Services Committee of the Legislature and the Governor on or before December 15, 2012.
